### ====================================
### TIPOS DE INFRACCION
### ====================================

### Ver todos los tipos (los 10 cargados por DataInitializer)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tipos
Accept: application/json

### Ver tipo por id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tipos/1
Accept: application/json

### Crear tipo nuevo
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tipos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "denominacion": "Conducción temeraria",
  "tipo": "Grave",
  "importeBase": 90000.0,
  "porcentajeDescuento": 0.0
}

### Actualizar tipo
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tipos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "denominacion": "Alcoholemia positiva actualizada",
  "tipo": "Grave",
  "importeBase": 85000.0,
  "porcentajeDescuento": 0.0
}

### Eliminar tipo
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tipos/11


### ====================================
### CONDUCTORES
### ====================================

### Ver todos los conductores
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conductores
Accept: application/json

### Crear conductor Sol
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conductores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Sol",
  "apellido": "Melocchi",
  "dni": "45678912",
  "domicilio": "Godoy Cruz, Mendoza",
  "numeroLicencia": "LIC-001"
}

### Crear conductor Ignacio
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conductores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Ignacio",
  "apellido": "Bertone",
  "dni": "43811825",
  "domicilio": "Lujan de Cuyo, Mendoza",
  "numeroLicencia": "LIC-002"
}

### Ver conductor por id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conductores/1
Accept: application/json


### ====================================
### INFRACCIONES
### ====================================

### Ver todas las infracciones
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/infracciones
Accept: application/json

### Crear infraccion (conductor id 1, tipo id 1 = Alcoholemia)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/infracciones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "descripcion": "Conductor detenido con 1.2 g/L de alcohol en sangre",
  "importe": 80000.0,
  "fecha": "2026-05-07",
  "conductor": { "id": 1 },
  "tipos": [{ "id": 1 }]
}

### Crear infraccion con 2 tipos (Alcoholemia + Sin cinturon)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/infracciones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "descripcion": "Múltiples infracciones detectadas",
  "importe": 110000.0,
  "fecha": "2026-05-07",
  "conductor": { "id": 2 },
  "tipos": [{ "id": 1 }, { "id": 4 }]
}

### Filtrar infracciones GRAVES
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/infracciones/tipo/Grave
Accept: application/json

### Filtrar infracciones MEDIAS
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/infracciones/tipo/Media
Accept: application/json

### Filtrar infracciones LEVES
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/infracciones/tipo/Leve
Accept: application/json

### Ver infracciones de conductor id 1
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/infracciones/conductor/1
Accept: application/json

### Eliminar infraccion
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/infracciones/1